<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٢-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ قَالَ حَدَّثَنَا مُهَنَّا قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَأَلْتُ أَحْمَدَ عَنِ الرَّجُلِ يَأْخُذُ مِنْ شَعْرِهِ وَمِنْ أَظْفَارِهِ أَيَدْفِنُهُ أَوْ يُلْقِيهِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> يَدْفِنُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> بَلَغَكَ فِيهِ شَيْءٌ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> كَانَ ابْنُ عُمَرَ يَدْفِنُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> عَنْ مَنْ هَذَا الْحَدِيثُ؟<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>⦗١٤١⦘<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">فَحَدَّثَنِي أَحْمَدُ:</span> عَنْ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ مَهْدِيٍّ عَنِ الْعُمَرِيِّ عَنْ نَافِعٍ عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ: كَانَ يَفْعَلُهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>